"{\"uid\": \"rferl.org-a-russia-france-macron-olympics-threat-32891053.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Share  Share  Print  French President Emmanuel Macron said on April 4 that he has no doubt Russia will malevolently target the Paris Olympics this summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 53, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 97, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999998348987583, \"rank\": 1.49241248502999e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have no doubt whatsoever, including in terms of information,\\\" Macron said in response to a question about whether he thought that Russia would try to target the Olympics.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1622378754057294e-14, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999998348987583, \"rank\": 1.49241248502999e-07, \"text\"